headline: Is It Too Late To Consider eBay (EBAY) After A 40% One Year Rally?
summary: If you are wondering whether eBay's current share price reflects its underlying worth, you are not alone; many investors are asking if the stock still offers value after a strong run. eBay's share price sits at US$90.91, with returns of 4.4% over the past week, 6.5% over the past month, 4.4% year to date, 40.1% over the last year, 108.2% over three years, and 79.0% over five years. This naturally raises questions about what is already priced in. Recent attention on eBay has centered on...
